== Rice Panicle Segmentation
We have developed a Gaussian mixture model based unsupervised image segmentation algorithm that can segment rice panicles. The proposed method outperforms existing methods like [https://plantmethods.biomedcentral.com/articles/10.1186/s13007-017-0254-7 Panicle-SEG] with an average F1 score greater than 80%. Next objective is to come up with a self-supervised algorithm on large dataset. 
- [https://plantmethods.biomedcentral.com/articles/10.1186/s13007-020-00567-8 ``Unsupervised Bayesian Learning for Rice Panicle Segmentation with UAV Images,''] /Plant Methods/, February 2020 \[[https://plantmethods.biomedcentral.com/track/pdf/10.1186/s13007-020-00567-8 pdf]] \[[https://github.com/i2pt/UBLRPSUI GitHub]] 
