== Stochastic Modeling of Wireless Network
We used [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Poisson_point_process Poisson point process (PPP)] and Hard-core poisson process (HCPP) to simulate BTS locations and evaluated various network parameters like throughput, SINR, outage probability using Monte Carlo simulation incorporating the idea of resource blocks. We used [http://www5.tu-ilmenau.de/nt/generic/paper_pdfs/D1.1.2.pdf WINNER II channel model] for path loss.
- [https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/7488044 On the downlink SINR and outage probability of stochastic geometry based LTE cellular networks with multi-class services] \[[pdf/hasan2015downlink.pdf pdf]] 
-- Best paper of ``3rd Student Paper Contest 2014", IEEE ComSoc Bangladesh Chapter.
